metatags.og:description:
Future Las Vegas CRE Broker - Retail || MDL Group - Retail Team || President - UNLV AMA || Executive Officer - UNLV AMA, REBS, RVF || Real Estate Major - UNLV Lee Business School · Viva Las Vegas? For me, it’s Viva ambition. 

I am Espen, a senior at UNLV majoring in Real Estate and minoring in Finance. As a transfer student from UNR, I bet on myself by moving to a city where I knew nobody, and I sure hit the jackpot here in Las Vegas by getting into commercial real estate. CRE is the perfect blend of helping businesses and having a tangible impact on my city, so why not get a degree in the field I'm most excited about? I currently work as the Junior Team Coordinator for the Retail Team at MDL Group, where I have gained firsthand experience in the commercial real estate industry, particularly in the retail asset class.
